            <title>[SOLR-985] TemplateString is not thread-safe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-985</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TemplateString is not thread-safe but it is being used concurrently by many cores due to the static instance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently TemplateString#cache is not synchronized, and static instance of TemplateString is used by VariableResolverImpl#replaceTokens().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
